    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> chives</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
