    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, remove the pan from heat and stir through the <strong>chopped chives</strong> and <strong>chopped basa</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy fish pie mix</strong></p><p>Transfer the<strong> creamy fish pie mix</strong> to an<strong> oven-proof dish</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
