            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the fish pie mix with the <strong>salt & vinegar chips</strong></p><p>Tip: Try to put the crispiest chips at the bottom and balance the rest over the top so that they don’t sink!</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 20-25 min or until the chips are crispy and the fish is cooked through</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
