        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pie is almost done, reboil half a kettle</p><p>Add your<strong> blanched peas</strong> to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 2-3 min or until tender</p><p>Once tender, drain the <strong>peas</strong> and return them to the pot with a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
